# API base URL (no trailing slash). Required for all environments.
#
# Local Docker (./scripts/deploy.sh local) - API at http://localhost/api
#   Simulator (same machine): http://localhost/api
#   Physical device (same LAN): use your machine IP, e.g. http://192.168.0.79/api
#   Add that origin to infra/docker/.env CORS_ORIGINS (and exp://... for Expo).
#
# Production: https://api.yourdomain.com
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost/api
